\nsufficiently many degrees of freedom) are approximately equal, no matter their\ninitial conditions, even when the system is not ergodic, as conjectured by\nKhintchine in 1943.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Apr 2014 20:58:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 03:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-09"}
